div.span: In this diagram; humans are custodians for the moral grammar of their acts by way of any agent. Ethical responsibility may be asserted by way of Incorporated Entities (persona ficta) whilst the inclusion of a Personal Data Storage Environment provided means in which to support artificial intelligence, privacy and dynamic informatics services by way of inferencing services; enables the means in which dynamic and temporally aware individual relationships may be rendered by way of human defined rules that make use of credentials; as to reduce the available granularity of informatics modifiers in a personally defined personable manner.

div.style: text-align: left
text-align: left
div.span: The systems propose to make use of cryptographic ledger technology, decentralised or otherwise; for the storage of 'commons' informatics as to include the interpretative values pertaining to the natural world and the context in which we live by association to social-concept such as 'law'.
